    "plan_content": "## Plan Summary\n\n**Root cause:** Classic off-by-one error in `src/utils.ts`, line 7.\n\n```ts\n// BUGGY — stops one iteration early, last item always skipped\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length - 1; i++) {\n\n// FIXED — iterates over all items including the last\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length; i++) {\n```\n\n**Change required:** Remove `- 1` from the loop condition. That's it — a single character change in one file.\n\n**Impact:** 3 of the 4 existing `processItems` tests in `tests/utils.test.ts` are currently failing and will all pass after the fix. The `sum` tests and the empty-array test are unaffected.",
